'''安德魯·巴席雅格'''（{{lang-en|Andrew D. Basiago}}，{{bd|1961年|9月18日||}}）是一名[[美國|美國]][[律師|律師]]，自稱曾參與過政府的秘密實驗。曾在[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年競選美國總統]]。

== 生平 ==
曾就讀[[加州大學洛杉磯分校|加州大學洛杉磯分校]]（1980年至1984年）和[[劍橋大學|劍橋大學]]。後在[[華盛頓州|華盛頓州]]從事律師行業<ref name="韋伯">{{cite book|author1=[[阿弗雷·韋伯|阿弗雷·韋伯]]著|coauthors=許淑媛譯|title=多次元宇宙|date=2017年7月|publisher=一中心有限公司|location=台中|isbn=978-986-94891-1-9}}</ref>。

自2004年起，巴席雅格一再地宣稱自己早年曾參與過政府的秘密計畫，並於2008年發布論文〈發現火星生命〉。他聲稱自己在7歲到12歲間加入[[國防高等研究計劃署|國防高等研究計劃署]]底下的「[[飛馬計畫|飛馬計畫]]」，參與過[[時光旅行|時光旅行]]實驗（巴席雅格稱其技術基於[[尼古拉·特斯拉|尼古拉·特斯拉]]的發明），包括穿梭到1863年[[亞伯拉罕·林肯|林肯]][[蓋茲堡演說|蓋茲堡演說]]的現場；而後在就讀大學時，又加入另一項[[中情局|中情局]]的秘密計畫，多次穿梭到[[火星|火星]]<ref name="韋伯" /><ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=TIME TRAVEL: US developed time travel at height of Cold War but was too dangerous to use|url=https://www.express.co.uk/news/science/889889/US-developed-time-travel-Project-Pegasus-at-height-of-Cold-War-Abraham-Lincoln-Gettysburg|accessdate=2021-01-21|date=2017-12-12|last=Deauville|first=Lara|work=Express.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204001611/https://www.express.co.uk/news/science/889889/US-developed-time-travel-Project-Pegasus-at-height-of-Cold-War-Abraham-Lincoln-Gettysburg|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Lawyer Says He Traveled Through Time and to Mars|url=http://www.yelmonline.com/news/local_news/article_1f52f842-26de-11e3-9fc7-0019bb2963f4.html|accessdate=2021-01-21|date=2013-09-26|publisher=Nisqually Valley News|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128151527/http://www.yelmonline.com/news/local_news/article_1f52f842-26de-11e3-9fc7-0019bb2963f4.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title='CIA used TIME TRAVEL foreseeing Trump win' Shock claims from ex-Presidential candidate|url=https://www.dailystar.co.uk/news/latest-news/trump-time-travel-john-titor-17069770|accessdate=2021-01-21|date=2016-11-20|last=O'Donoghue|first=Rachel|work=Dailystar.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128154743/https://www.dailystar.co.uk/news/latest-news/trump-time-travel-john-titor-17069770|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[星際政治學|星際政治學]]家[[阿弗雷·韋伯|阿弗雷·韋伯]]認可了巴席雅格的主張<ref name="韋伯" /><ref name=":0">{{cite news|title=穿越時空是真的？ 美律師稱乘時光機見過林肯！|url=https://www.ettoday.net/news/20120430/42906.htm|accessdate=2021-01-21|publisher=ETtoday新聞雲|date=2012-04-30|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128041722/https://www.ettoday.net/news/20120430/42906.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

巴席雅格還聲稱[[巴拉克·歐巴馬|巴拉克·歐巴馬]]在19歲時也是火星穿梭計畫的參與者。2012年1月3日，[[美國國安會|美國國安會]]發言人{{le|湯米·費艾托|Tommy Vietor}}否認了「歐巴馬去過火星」的指稱<ref name="韋伯" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=White House Denies President Obama Travelled To Mars Via Teleport At Age 19|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2012/01/04/white-house-denies-president-obama-travelled-to-mars_n_1183069.html?guccounter=1&guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8&guce_referrer_sig=AQAAAKI0urv7tA_SPS7_33nl8zEzY3Cbk6BwbrVJgUuWCdfkJ8oz2gaiwGR2YLV_KUzANL1Q7_mJaW9_nrP2tu8vHqJwPR5GhuG68Xe8pyosl__0cXS6ahmnmrQUMTNpZtoOy1jnnv3K5HAepeyIquPlwa8QRtFlz6zGqz1C6i4Yj2eX|accessdate=2021-01-21|date=2012-04-01|publisher=Huffington Post UK|language=en}}</ref>。

巴席雅格在2009年成立了火星異常現象研究協會（Mars Anomaly Research Society），並擔任總裁<ref>{{Cite web|title=Anomalous Martian anomalies|url=https://www.discovermagazine.com/the-sciences/anomalous-martian-anomalies|accessdate=2021-01-21|date=2009-01-07|publisher=Discover Magazine|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128035348/https://www.discovermagazine.com/the-sciences/anomalous-martian-anomalies|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年，巴席雅格作為[[獨立候選人|獨立候選人]]參選美國總統<ref>{{Cite web|title=I've been to Mars and it's full of ALIEN bodies claims lawyer in bid to be US President|url=https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/919501/I-went-Mars-littered-with-bodies-secret-space-program-Andrew-Basiago-MUFON|accessdate=2021-01-21|date=2018-02-15|last=Austin|first=Jon|publisher=Express.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128060644/https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/919501/I-went-Mars-littered-with-bodies-secret-space-program-Andrew-Basiago-MUFON|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Time-Traveling Truth Candidate for President Wins 1 Vote Locally|url=https://timesofsandiego.com/politics/2016/07/07/time-traveling-truth-candidate-for-president-wins-1-vote-locally/|accessdate=2021-01-21|date=2016-07-08|last=Stone|first=Ken|work=Times of San Diego|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128025606/https://timesofsandiego.com/politics/2016/07/07/time-traveling-truth-candidate-for-president-wins-1-vote-locally/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他主張的政策包括改造美國的電網、禁止[[化学尾迹阴谋论|化學尾跡]]、解密被隱匿的科技等<ref>{{Cite web|title=Time travel expert Andrew D. Basiago is running for president|url=https://www.metro.us/time-travel-expert-andrew-d-basiago-is-running-for-president/|accessdate=2021-01-21|date=2016-05-25|last=Metro|publisher=Metro US|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128135221/https://www.metro.us/time-travel-expert-andrew-d-basiago-is-running-for-president/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

